motionThreshold.title: Motion Threshold
motionThreshold.description: Number of meters moved in one frame before CCD is enabled

sweptSphereRadius.title: Swept Sphere Radius
sweptSphereRadius.description: This should be below the half extent of the collision volume. E.g. for and object of dimensions 1 meter, try 0.2

pathEasing.description: Any from: https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-tween#easing-methods - Copy it exactly without "pc."

functionName.title: Function
